== Bio 
I am currently a second-year Ph.D. student in ECE at UCLA, advised by Prof. [https://www.ee.ucla.edu/abeer-alwan Abeer Alwan]. My research area is speech processing, and automatic speech recognition in particular. \n
I received my Master's degree in Information and Communication Engineering from [https://english.bupt.edu.cn/ Beijing University of Posts and Telecommunications (BUPT)] in June 2019, advised by Prof. Gang Liu. I also got my Bachelor's degree in Communication Engineering from BUPT in June 2016.

